snippet: Kim Jong-un, the North Korean leader, also ordered his government to launch more rockets despite criticism from the United Nations Security Council, the Korean Central News Agency reported.
lead_paragraph: Kim Jong-un, the North Korean leader, also ordered his government to launch more rockets despite criticism from the United Nations Security Council, the Korean Central News Agency reported.
